<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Conrade Mollitor, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen haben, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu reden von des <expan>priest<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> sol <expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan>, und
                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss,
            was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen zu disem mal
            von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewr gnade werbe, daz ir in darinn
                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> verhörn, im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
            gelawben und nach notdurft der sache darczu tun wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
              <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>Vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
